texts.label: text
texts.orig: Upon the execution of this Agreement, MA shall pay to Company a quarterly service fee (the "Service Fee") in the amount equal to US $15,000.00 on the first day of each quarter for the Term of this Agreement as set forth in Section 1 hereinabove, for each month that MA has no sales pursuant to this Schedule A, with the first payment due and payable on the date of execution of this Agreement.
